## ðŸ”¹ About The Project
This is a **simple two-player dice game** where players roll dice and the highest number wins.  
Built with **vanilla JavaScript, HTML, and CSS**, this project is perfect for beginners to learn **DOM manipulation** and basic **randomization logic**.  

---

## ðŸ•¹ How to Play
1. Open `index.html` in your browser.  
2. Click the **Roll Dice** button.  
3. Two dice will appear with random numbers.  
4. The **winner** (Player 1 or Player 2) will be displayed dynamically.  
5. If both dice show the same number, itâ€™s a **draw**.

